data.description: Have you ever dreamed of owning a beautiful single-family home? If so, we have a great opportunity for you! Located at 307 Pardue Dr, Thomaston, GA 30286, this 1,613 sq ft home was built in 2019 and contains 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The exterior features a porch and walk-in closet, making it a great place to relax and enjoy the outdoors.  This is an amazing opportunity that won't last long.
